  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArticleDetailsFragment
    This class is the main Details fragment that is opened any time an article from the main RecyclerView is clicked.
    ArticleFavoritesDetailsFragment
    This class shows the details of any selected article from the Favorites list
    ArticleFavoritesListFragment
    This class is to display the articles that were added to the Favorites by the user.
    ArticleListFragment
    This class is the main RecyclerView that displays all the parsed article titles in a list to scroll through
    ArticleListFragment.Article
    This class is meant to hold information about each article that is parsed in order to display it in the List and in the Details Fragment
    ChargingDetailsFragment
    Contains information on how to load details in to the fragment and recycler view
    ChargingSecondPage
    This class provides functionality to the second page
    ChargingStationFragment
    this class contains information on how to laod information into the fragment and recycler view
    ChargingStationsMain
    this class provides functionality to the first page
    ChargingThirdPage
    This class provides functionality to the third page
    ExampleInstrumentedTest
    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.
    ExampleUnitTest
    Example local unit test, which will execute on the development machine (host).
    FinalOpenHelper
    FinalOpenHelper creates and manages the SQLite database for CST2335 Final Project Application Written for CST2335 Mobile Graphical Interface Programming Final Project Algonquin College August 8th, 2021
    MainActivity
    Main Activity for CST2335 Final Project Application.
    MovieDetailsFragment
    Class that holds an application fragment providing details of the searched input movie from the MovieSearchFragment class.
    MovieDetailsFragment.DownloadImageTask
    This class extends from AsyncTask to allow the execution and download of specifically the image given from the HTTP request from the movie database as a URL.
    MovieInfoActivity
    Class that holds an application page providing a tool bar and a navigation drawer to browse through options and between other internal applications on the app, as well as a fragment room to display each page below the toolbar.
    MovieSearchFragment
    Class that holds an application fragment providing an editText with user input for a movie to be searched and a Search button.
    OCTranspoActivity
    OCTranspoActivity allows users to track OCTranspo Bus Routes by Stop Number.
    RouteDetailsFragment
    Displays trip details for the selected route from the OCTranspo Server.
    SavedMovieDetailsFragment
    This class allows to obtain data from the movieInfo object that was selected by its position and display it in a fragment, just like MovieDetailsFragment.
    SavedMovieFragment
    This class withholds a layout with a recyclerview and using the database to populate it with the saved movies selected within the search option of MovieSearchFragment.
    SoccerGames
    This is the main activity class for the Soccer Articles API
    StopDetailsFragment
    Displays either the Add Stop layout or Stop Details layout depending on the value of stopNo.
    StopListFragment
    Displays stop numbers and descriptions stored in SQLite Database in a RecyclerView.
